{
  "stem": "1061.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That the more-- the only thing you can expect is more horror of another kind, you see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not necessarily it's the same that you went before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Could we stop at this point for a minute?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're almost-- we're almost done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were not liberated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because as it turns out, with the bombing and all, that camp had to be evacuated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you see, one more evacuation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Except this is not January, and there is no snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The month is April, 1945, end of April, 1945.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are lined up again, counted again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And those of us who were personal maids to the SS women have to carry their things, their rucksacks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't take anything of our own, but we had to carry their stuff.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were marched out of the camp somewhere, onto a road that was completely overrun with people of every kind-- of Germans, of, of German soldiers and German in uniform, out of uniform, and tanks and-- and horses, and the farmers with cows, and, and, and Polish POWs and Polish farmhands who worked the-- Polish, I meant Christian.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Christian Poles who were working the farms in-- in Germany during the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Slave labor, also, in-- of another kind, because they lived on the places where they worked.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, all that mixture, that whole conglomeration of people with us-- and not just us, but other camps being emptied-- all this mixed together.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, we were-- we were-- we had clothing that was marked with a big X, both at the front and on the back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So you could tell us a mile away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because this was white lacquer type of paint, huge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the way we were marked in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
